   96. Zsa-Zsa Gabor jailed for slapping Beverly Hills cop. 1990.
</P>
<P>
   97. Kilroy was everywhere. 1941-45.
</P>
<P>
   98. John Cougar Mellencamp drops Cougar. 1991.
</P>
<P>
