<SLUG> BC-GUATEMALA-U.S.-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE CIA AND GUATEMALA: THE SPIES WHO NEVER CAME IN FROM THE COLD
WAR 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
