   GLF-RYDER (Miami) _ Doral/Ryder Open, round three. By Malcom
Browne.
</P>
<P>
   RAC-SANTA-ANITA (Santa Anita, Calif.) _ The Santa Anita
Handicap, 5:45 p.m. Silver Charm and Free House.
</P>
<P>
   BOATING-FROSTBITING (Undated) _ When a day of boat racing means
the wind-chill is minus 15 and the water temperature can kill you,
recreational racers stay close to the fire while the truly
hard-core head for the water for a type of sailing known as
frostbiting. By Caitlin Kelly.
</P>
<P>
   OUTDOORS-MAINE-COD (Rockland, Maine) _ The depletion in cod
stocks in the Gulf of Maine inspired an industry-backed demand for
closure of the gulf by commercial fishermen. A compromise plan was
reached that allows some fishing for cod, but for how long? By Paul
Molyneaux.
</P>
</TEXT>
