<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    KASICH BOWLS OVER VOTERS IN IOWA
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    With AP photos.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AMES, Iowa _ John Kasich's ``Rolling Through Iowa'' tour of
bowling centers scored a strike this weekend among those looking
for a true man of the people in the Republican presidential field.
</P>
<P>
   ``I've got no zip,'' Kasich laughed Saturday after leaving a
